Class UnlimitedCache<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.codeleaf.common.behaviors.impl.UnlimitedCache<K,V>
  • Type Parameters:
    K - the type of the keys in the cache
    V - the type of the values in the cache
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cache<K,V>

    public final class UnlimitedCache<K,V>
extends Object
implements Cache<K,V>
    Provides a cache implementation without any limitations on memory usage. Internally leverages a HashMap.
